"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135328","Department of Health and Social Care","false","2019-07-04","<p>Detailed funding planning is underway for 2019-20 smoking cessation campaigns. Audited spend will be available at the end of the financial year.</p>","South Ribble","Seema Kennedy",,"2019-07-04T14:24:41.25Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135328/answer","Biography information for Seema Kennedy","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135328/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135328/answer",,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2019-06-27","Smoking: Health Education","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, how much funding his Department has committed to spend on campaigns to promote the cessation of smoking in 2019-20.","false","Biography information for Bob Blackman","Harrow East","Bob Blackman","270346"
