 Government what is the maximum speed of electric scooters on sale in the UK.","false","Biography information for Lord Jopling",,"Lord Jopling","HL16755"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135435","Home Office","false","2019-07-11","<p>Existing road traffic legislation applies to electric scooters. How the police enforce speed limits for electric scooters is an operational matter for individual Chief Officers of police in conjunction with local policing plans.</p>",,"Baroness Williams of Trafford",,"2019-07-11T16:32:36.95Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135435/answer","Biography information for Baroness Williams of Trafford","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135435/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1135435/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2019-06-27","Electric Scooters: Speed Limits","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government what steps they have taken to ensure that the police can enforce the legal speed limits for road users on the users of electric scooters especially those that travel at more than 20 miles per hour.","false","Biography information for Lord Jopling",,"Lord Jopling","HL16756"
